### Sign in as delivery boy
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
     "email":"nihal@mail.com",
    "password":"12345678"
}

### Get delivery boy profile
GET http://localhost:8000/api/delivery-boy/profile

### Update availability
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/delivery-boy/availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "isAvailable": true
}

### Update live location
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/delivery-boy/location
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "latitude": 12.9716,
    "longitude": 77.5946,
    "orderId": "PASTE_ORDER_ID_HERE"
}

### Get assigned orders
GET http://localhost:8000/api/delivery-boy/orders

### Update order status to dispatched
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/delivery-boy/orders/PASTE_ORDER_ID_HERE/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "dispatched"
}

### Update order status to delivered
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/delivery-boy/orders/PASTE_ORDER_ID_HERE/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "delivered"
}

### Get delivery boy earnings
GET http://localhost:8000/api/delivery-boy/earnings